    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "interesting. so u think the \"economic boost\" argument is basically a myth then? it just seems like it's used to push Estas laws through even if they hurt actual businesses. are there any actual studies or data that show it actually working, or is it always just a net loss for small towns?",
